Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 劃過天際的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理非常有效喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的提示是螃蟹和鯨魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.71,0:00:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能光憑外表判斷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.26,0:00:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.42,0:00:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.50,0:00:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹與鯨魚綁架事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.43,0:01:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天果然還是要喝啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣子光喝酒怎麼行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要吃點東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.92,0:02:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碎碎念嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.79,0:02:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.70,0:02:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽他說要到飯店吃飯 我才跟著來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道他只叫了酒還有下酒菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.81,0:02:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人帶小孩子到這個地方來 至少會叫點飯來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.05,0:02:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.27,0:02:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出一臉緊張的表情 一口啤酒也沒有喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你已經醉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有喝醉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.85,0:02:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到哪裡去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所不是在那個地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是遠藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把錢都準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有向警方報案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 我要再聽聽圭太的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…難道說是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點離開這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不能大聲說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生了綁架案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確像你所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能他孩子被綁架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛去是為了交付贖金的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 而且他好像還沒有聯絡警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.47,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機先生 緊跟著前面的計程車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.32,0:04:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要跟丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個牙醫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在該怎麼辦 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 先見了面把事情問清楚再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.09,0:05:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們不知道犯人會從什麼地方監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的住戶很有可能就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得要好好地想個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 我有個好方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來當病人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.37,0:05:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那就開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的牙齒好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.04,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,465)}好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,465)}你再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.23,0:05:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,465)}爸爸已經去拜託醫生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,465)}我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛到受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您休息了還來打擾真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我的孩子實在是因為牙痛的受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.93,0:05:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我牙齒好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以請你幫忙看看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請到醫院來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,465)}好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,465)}真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你還要叫到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請到診察室來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是偵探 名叫毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.45,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南聽到了我在講電話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤先生 方便的話能不能跟你談一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這孩子說的都是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意幫你盡點力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 也表示我們有緣分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說的沒錯 我的兒子是被人綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.29,0:06:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午他本來一個人在前院裡玩耍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太 我們到公園去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子在我們這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你報警的話他就沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會再聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.05,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人用的紙是一般的影印紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那後來犯人有沒有對你說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來打電話過來的是一個年輕的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.26,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要我在箱子裡放進三千萬的舊紙幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.92,0:07:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上6點在星光飯店的啤酒屋交付贖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是這麼指示我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.08,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我等待交付贖金的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6點過後 對方打電話過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.25,0:07:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我交易暫時取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人有沒有說這是為什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.34,0:07:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他們只說明天上午還會再來電話跟我聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是犯人那邊出了什麼意外吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們本來就不打算在今天拿贖金的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.01,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人從那個啤酒屋的某個地方觀察遠藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.86,0:08:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了確定他沒有報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 他們一開始打電話給你的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽到圭太的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹拜託他們才讓他聽電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.34,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 圭太那個時候的狀況怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的聲音意外地非常開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全感覺不出來有一點害怕的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.67,0:08:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說 小孩子都會哭著想要找媽媽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他媽媽已經不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的媽媽去年就病逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太向來跟幼稚園的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是這附近的鄰居太太都處得很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們也很疼愛圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 我就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.36,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這個犯人還有一個共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她還是一個帶慣了孩子的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就是由這個女人照顧圭太的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定真的被叔叔說對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不能安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.54,0:09:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過至少圭太在他們手上被殺的可能性降低了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.93,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情老實說我本來是應該和警方聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是警方介入的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有可能把犯人給抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.04,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…卻不能保證圭太是不是能平安回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.88,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在只有把希望放在你的身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.33,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以請你一定要讓圭太平安地回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你幫我這個忙好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這次主動談這件事的是我們這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會盡力把這件案子圓滿解決的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太謝謝你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.21,0:09:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們幾個現在恐怕沒有辦法繼續留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天晚上就先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.63,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那些犯人一定還會主動跟你電話聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片我就先借走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.91,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 你就不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.10,0:10:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會負責把圭太平平安安地帶回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這件事就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經裝了發信器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就等那些犯人的電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利偵探事務所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打電話來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那犯人說了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說還要把贖金增加兩千萬元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他們說數目太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給我兩個小時去籌錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有沒有聽到圭太的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確有照毛利先生說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他們讓圭太來聽電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他說的話莫名其妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太 你還好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 這裡有好多螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 我昨天跟你說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是亂說話的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.26,0:11:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鯨魚 那隻鯨魚還噴水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再跟你聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.07,0:11:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人真是這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.15,0:11:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤先生你就儘快去把錢湊齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果順利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想兩個小時之內就可以把圭太給帶回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這件事就全仰仗您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你掌握住犯人的線索了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.09,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太就在有很多螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還看得到鯨魚噴水的一個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹和鯨魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 那裡該不會是海邊附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太所在的位置看得到鯨魚噴水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總不能到小笠原那兒去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實圭太看到的根本就不是真的鯨魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該只是模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.51,0:12:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水族館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有鯨魚的模型啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.07,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像先生你看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.04,0:12:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的確有各式各樣的螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有鯨魚模型…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是別的水族館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了 我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實螃蟹說不定不是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.33,0:12:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為圭太在說有好多螃蟹的那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人不是說 你胡說什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定在那個犯人看起來 圭太眼中的東西根本不像螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說他打電話的地方不是水族館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鯨魚耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.86,0:13:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.01,0:13:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天日賣電視臺的推廣活動的主角是鯨魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太看到的那個鯨魚 難道會是那個鯨魚嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太就在能夠看到那個飛行船的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.05,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人打電話給遠藤先生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個飛行船正好飛到米花公園的正上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米花公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 昨天他們說要贖人的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是在米花鎮的飯店裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回到米花鎮找找看什麼地方有很多螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.65,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信圭太一定就在那附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.23,0:14:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.77,0:14:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人說不定已經打電話聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說犯人兩分鐘之前去過電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.69,0:14:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指示遠藤先生在空宿車站的一號月臺的最前面等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.60,0:14:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空宿車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你就在這裡繼續找螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叔叔他們沒有抓到犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那箱子上面裝了發信器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.81,0:15:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候還可以掌握犯人的正確位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人會不會叫遠藤先生坐到電車上面去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有這個可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想他們也許是要在別的地方交錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把箱子丟過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不管你的孩子了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.37,0:15:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.69,0:16:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是毛利先生已經把他摩托車的號碼拍下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該很快就知道犯人的身份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.91,0:16:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號一直在同一個地方沒有移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們藏身的地方就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了那個轉角就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們是在這個地方換了別的箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.39,0:16:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然叔叔已經把犯人的摩托車的號碼拍下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個也是犯人的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會車號還有車牌都是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.97,0:16:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是犯人回去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們拿到錢就可能把圭太給…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.78,0:17:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且同時可以看得到鯨魚飛行船的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得圭太說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻鯨魚還噴水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鯨魚飛行船是不可能噴水的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.79,0:17:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道圭太看見的不是飛行船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.55,0:17:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡的話就看不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.97,0:17:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從星光飯店那裡說不定就可以看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米花公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太就是看到那個清潔工廠煙囪冒的煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到那副景象的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.83,0:18:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在清潔工廠跟米花公園連成一條直線的延長線上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是這附近了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這個高度還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說真的要看起來像是鯨魚在噴水的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟飛行船同一個高度才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個飯店裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子和椅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他說的螃蟹是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 是螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些桌子和椅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果從上面看起來就像是螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.49,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太就在這個飯店裡的某個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.97,0:19:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳知道這個孩子住在哪一個房間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子他住在下面一層樓的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他剛才已經和他爸爸媽媽回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.95,0:19:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 被我逮到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太還平安無事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.25,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人鐵拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的要把這個孩子殺掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很煩啊 怎麼又開始婦人之仁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.37,0:20:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人是綁架犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.54,0:20:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把他們抓起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.27,0:20:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要是動一下我就殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.94,0:20:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.85,0:20:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可以踢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.51,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面不遠停了一輛摩托車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了這個門之後就跑起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.98,0:21:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.67,0:22:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.11,0:22:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.23,0:22:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.03,0:23:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你怎麼找到這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.30,0:23:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧合啦巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.20,0:23:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我是來找螃蟹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.73,0:23:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛好就發現圭太了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.82,0:23:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來因為我嚇了一大跳叫了一聲綁架犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.48,0:23:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個犯人就匆匆忙忙地跑了出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.78,0:23:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變成那樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.19,0:23:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.12,0:23:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.82,0:23:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.47,0:23:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經聽柯南說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.45,0:23:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道有綁架案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不立刻通知我們警方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.75,0:23:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你們根本不信任我們警方嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.76,0:23:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 絕對沒有這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.47,0:23:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 叔叔用了整整一個小時的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在對目暮警官解釋這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.38,0:23:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾為之也不錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.44,0:23:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.16,0:23:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.34,0:23:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子是不可能到外面去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.87,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個地方會有血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.75,0:24:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生田先生是站在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.92,0:24:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.08,0:24:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.56,0:24:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜路殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.06,0:24:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ne…Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.78,0:24:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香菸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.72,0:24:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也是很驚人的手法喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.79,0:24:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看清楚黑暗中的殺人嗎?
